{"tid":681664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鬆獅危掛　籮大卡窗救一命","createTime":"2018-05-28T08:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T09:52:57.000Z","uid":163401,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"224b8237581ac683837a99c2dfec03290aba2b77","tid":681664,"uid":163401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:40:19.000Z","msg":"「喂！有咩慢慢講，你入返嚟先！」上環有人企跳，啊！係有狗企跳先啱！呢隻Chow Chow（鬆獅犬）因咩事睇唔開呀？講出嚟聽吓！<br />\n原來噚日上晝11點幾，呢隻住喺皇后大道中中源中心5樓嘅Chow Chow哥，趁主人唔喺屋企周圍跳，仲伸個頭出窗，點知因為太過肥，想縮返入屋嗰陣，竟然卡住咗，好彩有動物義工發現報警。<br />\n由動物義工提供嘅片段可以見到，Chow Chow哥吊喺外牆，前腳不停爬吓爬吓，睇見都覺牙煙。Chow Chow哥嚇到係咁吠，當時烈日當空，熱到佢伸晒脷，真係陰公豬！多得佢個肥美屁股頂一頂，先冇跌落街咋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180528/large/a1005a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180528%2Flarge%2Fa1005a.gif&h=58aa8786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鬆獅吊喺外牆，前腳不停掙扎，其後被消防救回。<br />\n動物義工提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n由消防救回　現中暑症狀<br />\n<br />\n消防趕到準備破門入屋時，咁啱遇着主人返嚟，消防成功救狗狗入屋，真係險過剃頭，Chow Chow嚇到成身震晒，仲有疑似中暑症狀，但好彩冇受傷，主人陪同送愛協獸醫診所治療。警方懷疑主人離家時窗戶冇關上，而隻成年雄性Chow Chow懷疑貪玩跳出窗外，好彩後腳勾住窗框，先冇跌落街。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180528&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20403660\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180528%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20403660&d=bFYDW4yt9lkxTqnDWxBjIjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0fda44f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180528%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20403660&h=dbc1c24a\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180528&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20403660</a>"},{"pid":"4c1c5e4094e76b44458789d175e968cc9b8845be","tid":681664,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"077cb042288c33060270c59e1ca18e398e62b7f4","tid":681664,"uid":99960,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208564c07c667f7165cefd18af87228fcd9d9c07","tid":681664,"uid":163401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/164249_88490de4cea338da01896269d90370bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F164249_88490de4cea338da01896269d90370bc.png&h=6446ff50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c16208b887ad74f083188b68c617e5a1570c3dd0","tid":681664,"uid":45914,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:43:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57be0c6fe320ec2939fa278eef1064b46c92b8e4","tid":681664,"uid":160662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:44:06.000Z","msg":"樓主咁睇唔開啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080c26154c740089bc38a5326c517d16938b2abe","tid":681664,"uid":78971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  蘿大執返條命"},{"pid":"c2db8b965b9a887927c430a3a0fd48121e1cfffb","tid":681664,"uid":95123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:06:38.000Z","msg":"動物義工必須死"},{"pid":"c4678034bbf2f11070a18cffe880ba2304edaa4b","tid":681664,"uid":156005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:12:07.000Z","msg":"樓主個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361e0e46ade79df87ec771b2a56acbd3bda027c5","tid":681664,"uid":163401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57be0c6fe320ec2939fa278eef1064b46c92b8e4","tid":681664,"uid":160662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:44:06.000Z","msg":"樓主咁睇唔開啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:39:58.000Z","msg":"我只係想睇下我個狗奴才返黎未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e6497ac3d34d9b1d381b0ab12dc3d6b67dea454","tid":681664,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:51:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659b1d6481e762f0c1b5b81cc85bf56e570bc8d6","tid":681664,"uid":15730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T09:52:57.000Z","msg":"好得意呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}